And yet, it's all worth it to see these stars' characters transformations in some of the finest examples of makeup artistry, special effects and costume design. Check out these incredible movie makeovers ... From glamorous Hollywood veteran to bewitching witch! Meryl Streep has undergone quite the transformation for her latest role. The three-time Oscar winning actress is starring as The Witch in the Disney big-screen adaption of the musical "Into The Woods," a twist on the beloved Brothers Grimm fairy tales. While Streep's Witch wishes to reverse a curse so that her beauty may be restored, luckily the Hollywood actress will be back to her glamorous self in no time. The film is due to release on Dec. 25, 2014.
